Do not use them, they do not know what they are doing. I now possess a motorcycle that I can never sell and if I ever laps the tags I can never tag it again since I don't own the vehicle that I paid off in full. Refund my money and come get your bike. Or send me a new bike with a clear title that does not have a lean assigned to it. This has been over a year now, you need to get your business in order or stop trying to do business.
